<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_82_r1l5">Edler lıeber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> als vns eẅr edel <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Jacob <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l6">Juden vnd <expan>vnt<ex>er</ex>ſeſſen</expan> vnd der <expan>ſecklın<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns wonhaft etc das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l7"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır dıe <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>ſecklin<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l8">ſache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> . dıe wır in <expan>ſund<ex>er</ex>heıt</expan> ʒu Jr <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ʒu <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> handen <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l9">vnd als der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Jacob eẅr Jud meynt daʒ er an der <expan>ſecklin<ex>n</ex></expan> hawſe vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l10">gut ein mıterb ſey etc / Da ıſt vns nıht <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von / VVıe <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l11">deẅht <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> Jacob Juden / daʒ er ʒu dem <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> gute . <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ʒu <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> bey </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l12">vns des wır mechtıg ſein ıcht ʒu <expan>ſpreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett / ſo <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wır Jm <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l13"><expan>ſeine<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>ſcheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mıt <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt vmb <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>wıll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . ſleẅnıgs </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l14"><expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey vns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> / Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lıeb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_82_r1l15"><expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vȷ<hi rend="sup">a</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_82" id="40r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hartman von
                        <expan>Cronemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als uns ewr edel
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat von
                            <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> Jacob, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>s</expan> juden
                        und <expan>unt<ex>er</ex>sessen</expan>, und der
                            <expan>Secklin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> bey uns wonhaft etc., das
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                            <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        die <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Secklin<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>jüdin<ex>n</ex></expan> von sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, die
                        wir in <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>heit</expan> zu ir
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> zu <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> handen
                                <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> und als der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> Jacob ewr jud meynt, daz er an der
                                <expan>Secklin<ex>n</ex></expan> hawse und gut ein miterb sey etc,
                        da ist uns niht <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> von. Wie
                                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> dewht
                            <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Jacob juden, daz er zu dem
                                <expan>obg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> gute <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        zu <expan>yema<ex>n</ex>t</expan> bey uns, des wir mechtig sein, icht zu
                                <expan>spreche<ex>n</ex></expan> hett, so
                            <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>will<ex>e</ex>n</expan> slewnigs <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> bey
                        uns <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> helffen
                            <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>. Denn wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>.</ab>
</div>
